fields.invitation_text_subject: Welcome to a study at The Economic Science Institute.
fields.invitation_text:
[subject name],

Welcome to the study

The study starts on:
[start date]

The study lasts for:
[number of days] days, ending on [end date]

Use this link to log in:
[log in link]

Keep this email, you need to follow this link to log in each day.

Do not share this link with others.

If you have trouble logging in, do not reply to this email, please contact:
[contact email]

Thanks for your participation!
fields.cancelation_text:
[subject name],

Unfortunately, we had to cancel the online Fitbit study you have been participating in.

No further action is required on your part.

If you have any questions, do not reply to this email, please contact:
[contact email]

Thank you for your understanding.
